These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-1::.
4 different pets are kept: pony, lizard, horse, turtle
1. the owner of the pony is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
2. the owner of the lizard is somewhere between the owner of the horse and the owner of the turtle##7
3. the owner of the horse is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |  2   |   3   |  4   |
| Pet   | horse | lizard | turtle | pony |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-2::.
There 4 different types of food: cranberry, cucumber, apple, pepper
1. the person eating apple is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
2. the person eating apple is somewhere between the person eating cucumber and the person eating cranberry##7
3. the person eating apple is between the person eating cucumber and the person eating pepper##2

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Food   | cranberry | pepper | apple | cucumber |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-3::.
