1. the person eating lime is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
2. the person eating strawberry is somewhere between the person eating potato and the person eating spinach##7
3. the person eating potato is somewhere to the right of the person eating strawberry##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |  2   |    3    |   4    |
| Food   | lime | spinach | strawberry | potato |

