.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-4::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, helicopter, motorbike, car
1. the person driving the car is somewhere between the person driving the motorbike and the person driving the helicopter##7
2. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the left of the person driving the car##5
3. the person driving the skateboard is between the person driving the car and the person driving the motorbike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |   3   |    4    |
| Transport   | motorbike | skateboard | car | helicopter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, epic, western, romance
1. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
2. the person watching epic movies is between the person watching adventure movies and the person watching romance movies##2
3. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
4. the person watching adventure movies is somewhere between the person watching western movies and the person watching romance movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |   3   |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | western | adventure | epic | romance |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, brazilian, dutch, pakistani
1. the canadian is somewhere between the pakistani and the brazilian##7
2. the dutch is somewhere between the canadian and the pakistani##7
3. the dutch is on the left or right of the pakistani##3
4. the dutch is somewhere to the right of the pakistani##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |     3     |    4    |
| Nationality   | pakistani | dutch | canadian | brazilian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-7::.
