1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere between the person drinking lemonade and the person drinking tea##7
2. the person drinking juice is somewhere between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person drinking lemonade##7
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |    2     |   3   |      4      |
| Beverage   | tea | hot-chocolate | juice | lemonade |

