3. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the car##1
4. the person driving the car is somewhere between the person driving the taxi and the person driving the bus##7

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |  3  |    4    |
| Transport   | bus | trike | car | taxi |

